    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">findim</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">Î </span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">K</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span> <span class=\"n\">u_2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">V</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span> <span class=\"n\">u_1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">field</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_comm_group</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">vector_space</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">],</span> <span class=\"n\">â„•</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Everything that comes after <code>V</code>.</p>",
        "id": 221631905,
